Revision history for XML-LibXML-Ferry

v0.8.4  2018-01-20
        Add support for namespaced attributes

v0.8.3  2018-01-19
        Bugfix: use hasChildNodes() instead of counting
        Feature: fully handle mixes of text and element children
        Add textNodeContent() for immediate text node contents only

v0.8.0  2018-01-18
        Add toHash() methods to help compare XML trees

v0.7.2  2018-01-17
        Bugfix: always require third-party modules

v0.7.1  2018-01-16
        First public release

